	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Reaction</strong>  - 1 @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.IXk7hfrAoVQU3dLJ]{Ki Point} - Magical​</p><br><p><em>Trigger​: You are hit by an attack (anything that requires an attack roll, including some spells).​</em></p><ul><li><p>Roll your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.4km0TjS91nC4PBNL]{Martial Arts} damage die and add your monk level.</p></li><li><p>You reduce the incoming damage by the amount of damage you rolled.</p></li><li><p>If you reduce the damage to 0, you can redirect the attack:</p><ul><li><p>If the attack was a melee attack, make an @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.aaftAEUfyNoAbFS3]{unarmed attack} (again) against a creature within 5 ft. of you.</p></li><li><p>If the attack was a ranged attack, this attack has a 60 ft. range.</p></li><li><p>Either way, your redirected attack is the same damage type as the original attack you deflected.</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
